title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 645-4.14 - Penalties and sanctions
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 645-4.14 - Penalties and sanctions

State Regulations

Any final order issued by the commission pursuant to the
procedures specified in this Subpart may include civil penalties and
administrative sanctions to the full extent provided by ECL, section
71-3303. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
645-4.14

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
